    "content": "<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"he\" dir=\"rtl\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\">\n  <title>מסך התחברות</title>\n  <style>\n    * { box-sizing: border-box; }\n    body {\n      margin: 0;\n      min-height: 100vh;\n      display: grid;\n      place-items: center;\n      font-family: \"Segoe UI\", Arial, sans-serif;\n      background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 10%, #74f7ff55, transparent 28%),\n                  linear-gradient(135deg, #07111f, #13284b 55%, #23133d);\n      color: #f7fbff;\n    }\n    .login {\n      width: min(92vw, 390px);\n      padding: 28px;\n      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.18);\n      border-radius: 22px;\n      background: rgba(8,18,38,.72);\n      box-shadow: 0 28px 80px rgba(0,0,0,.38);\n      backdrop-filter: blur(18px);\n    }\n    h1 { margin: 0 0 8px; font-size: 30px; }\n    p { margin: 0 0 24px; color: #b9c8dc; line-height: 1.5; }\n    label { display: block; margin: 14px 0 7px; color: #dceaff; font-weight: 700; }\n    input {\n      width: 100%;\n      min-height: 48px;\n      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.18);\n      border-radius: 14px;\n      padding: 0 14px;\n      background: rgba(255,255,255,.08);\n      color: #fff;\n      outline: none;\n    }\n    input:focus { border-color: #66efff; box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(102,239,255,.14); }\n    button {\n      width: 100%;\n      min-height: 50px;\n      margin-top: 22px;\n      border: 0;\n      border-radius: 16px;\n      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #62f1ff, #9d7dff);\n      color: #06101f;\n      font-weight: 900;\n      cursor: pointer;\n    }\n    .links { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; gap: 12px; margin-top: 16px; }\n    a { color: #83efff; text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px; }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <main class=\"login\">\n    <h1>ברוך הבא</h1>\n    <p>התחבר כדי להמשיך לאפליקציה שלך.</p>\n    <form>\n      <label for=\"email\">אימייל</label>\n      <input id=\"email\" type=\"email\" autocomplete=\"email\" placeholder=\"name@example.com\" required>\n      <label for=\"password\">סיסמה</label>\n      <input id=\"password\" type=\"password\" autocomplete=\"current-password\" placeholder=\"••••••••\" required>\n      <button type=\"submit\">כניסה</button>\n      <div class=\"links\">\n        <a href=\"#\">שכחתי סיסמה</a>\n        <a href=\"#\">יצירת חשבון</a>\n      </div>\n    </form>\n  </main>\n</body>\n</html>\n",
